- Koyeb async pattern: `apps/backend/src/deploy/koyeb.ts:604-624`
- Frontend polling infrastructure: `apps/web/src/hooks/useDeploymentStatus.ts:25-84`
- Database schema: `apps/backend/src/db/schema.ts:28`

